content: Good morning! Welcome to the technical round of the interview. I'm Jeyachandran, the hiring officer. Thank you for taking the time to speak with me today. Before we begin, I'd like to take a look at your resume. Can you walk me through your experience as a React Developer at SKEWESS TECH, specifically the project you developed for an online signing system? What were some of the key challenges you faced, and how did you overcome them?
